  "remarks": "Al-Qaida (QE.A.4.01.) facilitator, courier and operative. As of 2010, facilitated activities for senior Pakistan-based Al-Qaida operatives. Reportedly killed in a drone strike on 1 October 2012 in Waziristan, Pakistan. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021.; Listing: Listed by UN 1989 Committee on 14 March 2012 (amended on 15 Nov. 2021, 11 Mar. 2025).",
